        <abstract> 
<p>CD is ashamed of length of <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi> – with index, nearly 600 pages. JVC will be awfully sick of ch. 1.</p>  
<p>In intervals of correcting proofs, he is writing on the formation of vegetable mould through the action of worms. It will be a curious little book [<hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
